Subject: How to Lay a Crepe Wool Facial Hair
Description: Learn basic hair laying techniques used in special effects and costuming to create the look of inexpensive, realistic facial hair. Techniques will be demonstrated on a volunteer, and supplies will be discussed.  Speakers include:Melissa Ebbe - Track: Costuming  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: none
